# Linko (CLI)

Linko ye simple social network project hast ke ba C++ neveshte shode.
In version faghat console (CLI) hast.

## Features
- Register / Login / Logout
- Create post
- Edit post (only author mitune edit kone)
- Follow users
- Like and Comment
- Search users
- Block / Unblock
- Save & Load data az file

## Project Structure
- core/ : logic asli system (User, Post, Network, FileManager, ...)
- cli/  : command line interface

## Description
In project bar asas class ha design shode va har bakhsh masooliyat khodesh ro dare.
User baraye modiriat karbaran,
Post baraye modiriat post ha,
Network baraye logic asli system.
